hh3cLAG.name: hh3cLAG
hh3cLAG.contactinfo: Platform Team Hangzhou H3C Tech. Co., Ltd. Hai-Dian District Beijing P.R. China http://www.h3c.com Zip:100085

hh3cAggLinkTable.name: hh3cAggLinkTable
hh3cAggLinkTable.description: A table of aggregate link objects.

hh3cAggLinkNumber.name: hh3cAggLinkNumber
hh3cAggLinkNumber.description: The serial number of aggregation group.

hh3cAggLinkMode.name: hh3cAggLinkMode
hh3cAggLinkMode.description: Type of aggregation. manual: Manual aggregation, no LACP. static: Membership specified by user, LACP is used to validate. dynamic: Completely dynamic aggregation detected by LACP.

hh3cAggLinkPortList.name: hh3cAggLinkPortList
hh3cAggLinkPortList.description: List of ports in this link aggregation group, by bridge port number. If the mode of the link aggregation group is manual or static, you can update this list to your hearts content. However, if the link aggregation group is dynamic, the system will maintain it. You are not permitted to set the value of this to all zeroes.

hh3cAggLinkState.name: hh3cAggLinkState
hh3cAggLinkState.description: RowStatus, now support three states: createAndGo, active, destroy.

hh3cAggPortListSelectedPorts.name: hh3cAggPortListSelectedPorts
hh3cAggPortListSelectedPorts.description: A PortList of physical ports that have been selected but not attached to this aggregator. When the bit is set to 1,it means the corresponding port is in the portlist.

hh3cAggPortListSamePartnerPorts.name: hh3cAggPortListSamePartnerPorts
hh3cAggPortListSamePartnerPorts.description: PortList of physical ports that have the same Actor SystemID and partner systemID as this aggregator, but have different actor and partner keys of aggregator.

hh3cAggPortTable.name: hh3cAggPortTable
hh3cAggPortTable.description: A table of aggregate port objects.

hh3cAggPortIndex.name: hh3cAggPortIndex
hh3cAggPortIndex.description: Port ifindex which is according to RFC1213 MIB.

hh3cAggPortNotAttachedReason.name: hh3cAggPortNotAttachedReason
hh3cAggPortNotAttachedReason.description: Reason why this port is selected for an aggregator but not attached, 0: The port is attached to this aggregator. 1: The current number of active ports has reached the upper limit. 2: All aggregation resources are already in-use. 3: The port's configuration is improper for being attached. 4: The port's partner is improper for being attached. 5: The number of current active ports has not reached the lower limit. 6: The port's physical state (down) is improper for being attached. 7: The port is not selected for an aggregator. 8: The port's hardware restriction is improper for being attached. 9: The port's speed is improper for being attached. 10: The port's duplex mode is improper for being attached.

hh3cAggPortLacpState.name: hh3cAggPortLacpState
hh3cAggPortLacpState.description: Control ports' lacp enble or disable.

hh3cAggPortNotAttachedString.name: hh3cAggPortNotAttachedString
hh3cAggPortNotAttachedString.description: The string which interprets this port is selected for an aggregator but not attached.

hh3cAggResourceAllocationValue.name: hh3cAggResourceAllocationValue
hh3cAggResourceAllocationValue.description: The priority value calculated to decide which aggregations have first call on the load-sharing aggregation resources in the hardware. It depends on the aggregation type and total speed.

hh3cAggSpeedChangedNotification.name: hh3cAggSpeedChangedNotification
hh3cAggSpeedChangedNotification.description: This event will be triggered whenever an aggregation changes its speed.

hh3cAggPortInactiveNotification.name: hh3cAggPortInactiveNotification
hh3cAggPortInactiveNotification.description: This event will be triggered whenever any port in aggregator is made inactive.

hh3cAggPortInactiveNotification2.name: hh3cAggPortInactiveNotification2
hh3cAggPortInactiveNotification2.description: This event will be triggered whenever the port in aggregator is made inactive.

hh3cAggPortActiveNotification.name: hh3cAggPortActiveNotification
hh3cAggPortActiveNotification.description: This event will be triggered whenever the port in aggregator is made active.

hh3cLAGMibCompliance.name: hh3cLAGMibCompliance
hh3cLAGMibCompliance.description: The compliance statement for SNMP entities which implement the Lag MIB.

hh3cLAGMibObjectGroup.name: hh3cLAGMibObjectGroup
hh3cLAGMibObjectGroup.description: The collection of objects which are used to represent LAG objects.

hh3cLAGMibNotificationGroup.name: hh3cLAGMibNotificationGroup
hh3cLAGMibNotificationGroup.description: The collection of objects which are used to represent notifications.
